18  import org.gradoop.temporal.model.impl.operators.matching.TemporalTestData;

20  import java.util.ArrayList;
21  import java.util.Collection;
22  
23  public class HomomorphismOverlapsData implements TemporalTestData {
24    @Override
25    public Collection<String[]> getData() {
26      ArrayList<String[]> data = new ArrayList<>();
27  
28      // 1.[(Stanton St & Chrystie St) -[e8]-> (Hancock St & Bedford Ave)
29      //      (E15 St & Irving Pl)-[e3]->(Washington Park)]
30      data.add(new String[] {
31        "Overlaps_HOM_1_default_citibike",
32        "MATCH (a)-[e1]->(b) (c)-[e2]->(d) WHERE e1.edgeId=8 AND NOT e1.val.overlaps(e2.val)",
33        "expected1",
34        "expected1[(s12)-[e8]->(s13) (s3)-[e3]->(s4)]"
35      });
36  
37      // identical edges overlap, too
38      // 1.[(Broadway & W29) -[edgeId:7]-> (8 Ave & W 31)
39      //          (Broadway & W29) -[edgeId:19]->(8 Ave & W31)]
40      // 2.[(Broadway & W29) -[edgeId:7]-> (8 Ave & W 31)
41      //          (Broadway & W29) -[edgeId:7]->(8 Ave & W31)]
42      // 3.[(Broadway & W29) -[edgeId:19]-> (8 Ave & W 31)
43      //           (Broadway & W29) -[edgeId:19]->(8 Ave & W31)]
44      // 4.[(Broadway & W29) -[edgeId:19]-> (8 Ave & W 31)
45      //           (Broadway & W29) -[edgeId:7]->(8 Ave & W31)]
46      data.add(new String[] {
47        "Overlaps_HOM_2_default_citibike",
48        "MATCH (a)-[e1]->(b) (a)-[e2]->(b) WHERE a.id=486 AND e1.val.overlaps(e2.val)",
49        "expected1,expected2,expected3,expected4",
50        "expected1[(s21)-[e13]->(s11) (s21)-[e13]->(s11)], " +
51          "expected2[(s21)-[e13]->(s11) (s21)-[e19]->(s11)], " +
52          "expected3[(s21)-[e19]->(s11) (s21)-[e13]->(s11)], " +
53          "expected4[(s21)-[e19]->(s11) (s21)-[e19]->(s11)]"
54      });
55  
56      // 1.[(Hicks St & Montague)-[edgeId:2]->(Hicks St & Montague)
57      //           (W37 St & 4 Ave)-[edgeId:5]->(Hicks St & Montague)]
58      data.add(new String[] {
59        "Overlaps_HOM_3_default_citibike",
60        "MATCH (a)-[e1]->(b) (c)-[e2]->(b) WHERE b.id=406 " +
61          "AND e1.val_from.before(e2.val_from) " +
62          "AND e2.val.overlaps(e1.val)",
63        "expected1",
64        "expected1[(s2)-[e2]->(s2) (s7)-[e5]->(s2)]"
65      });
66  
67      // 1.[(Hicks St & Montague)->(Hicks St & Montague)]
68      // 2.[(Broadway & E14 St) -> (S5 Pl & S5 St)]
69      // 3.[(Broadway & W24 St) -[edgeId:0]-> (9 Ave & W18)]
70      // 4.[(Broadway & W24 St) -[edgeId:1]-> (9 Ave & W18)]
71      // 5.[(Lispenard St & Broadway) -> (Broadway & W51 St)]
72      data.add(new String[] {
73        "Overlaps_HOM_4_default_citibike",
74        "MATCH (a)-[e]->(b) WHERE " +
75          "e.val.overlaps(Interval(Timestamp(2013-06-01T00:00:00), Timestamp(2013-06-01T00:01:00))) OR " +
76          "e.val.overlaps(Interval(Timestamp(2013-06-01T00:36:00), " +
77          "Timestamp(2013-06-01T00:37:00)))",
78        "expected1,expected2,expected3,expected4,expected5",
79        "expected1[(s2)-[e2]->(s2)], expected2[(s8)-[e6]->(s9)], expected3[(s0)-[e0]->(s1)]," +
80          "expected4[(s0)-[e1]->(s1)], expected5[(s28)-[e18]->(s29)]"
